content:
It’s so funny how people can’t take being treated like they treat you. 
When you switch it up on they ass and give them the same energy back they be so hurt. 
You get what you give.
Meanwhile the birds are chirping, the sun is shining, your coins are rolling, and that smile on your face ain’t going NOWHERE!
Long story short be careful who you fuck over. When they hit you with that “I’m good Luv, Enjoy” you might not be able to handle it.
